Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 任务完成!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 开始庆功宴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯!
